                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-266-off1457 t18280529-266-cd1458"></join>, 1 watch, value 3l.; 2 gold seals, value 1l.,; 1 gold key, value 7s.; 2 jackets, value 1l. 10s.; 4 shirts, value 12s.; 1 handkerchief, value 1s.; 1 waistcoat, value 4s., and 1 pair of trousers, value 8s., the goods of 
